content.rendered:
Defero

A secure service for the formation and analysis of the users financial report

About

Brand: Defero

Location: Oslo, Norway

Industry: Fintech

Budget: $200,000

Clutch Review: 

5.0
 5/5

Product link: defero.no  

Type of software: Web App (SaaS)

Scope of work: Back-end, Front-end, UI/UX Design, Project Management, Quality Assurance

Defero is a secure service for the formation and analysis of the users financial report. It provides an opportunity to fulfill periodic monitoring, to obtain a statistical and objective assessment of their financial activities.

Key features

  • Create a service that allows users to receive a financial activity report on a monthly basis, based on a statistical and objective assessment.​
  • Allow users to view their own Score and its dynamics during the selected period, and see their income and expense statistics.​
  • System for daily updates of the report
  • Create a Defero Points (DP) Accumulation System, where users can use site partner offers.
  • Develop an AI recommendation system using DynamicYield for better selection of banks based on financial analysis of own funds
  • Develop a system of levels (gamification), which will depend on different user actions.

Technologies

Laravel 5.7

PHP 7.2

Postgres DB

Redis 5

Vue 2.5+

Elasticsearch

DynamicYield

Digitalocean

SCSS

Gitlab

What our client
wanted

Eigil Arff Tarjem

Chief Executive Officer

We hired QT Global to develop our website from scratch. We needed to create a platform that provides individuals with their private credit reports

Functional
features

The ability to receive financial activity report.​
A monthly update report based on statistical and objective assessment.​
Possibility for users after registering in the system to see their own Score, as well as the average Score in their place of residence and in Norway in general.​
The ability to view the dynamics of your Score during the selected period, as well as see your income and expense statistics.​
Secure two-step registration: users confirm their identity through authorization in the bankID system, after which they add their phone number and password in the system.​
The opportunity for users to accumulate Defero Points (DP) and use them for using various offers of site partners.​
The system of levels (gamification) of users which depends on various actions that they do on the site (for example, fill in all the fields, invite friends, follow the listed links).​

DynamicYield AI recommendation system for better selection of banks based on financial analysis

Business value

  • 500,000 app members as of January 2023
  • Dozens of attracted affiliate partners - banks and investment companies
  • M&A with AXO Group - one of the top European digital brokers for personal lending
  • $ 759.1K of attracted investments during the Pre-Seed round
  • Expansion to Sweden and Finland as separate web applications

Client’s review

Eigil Arff Tarjem

CEO at Defero AS

QT Global met expectations, delivering high-quality work. They excel at understanding our business. We have an open dialogue, and even being offshore, they speak English quite well. They’re honest and let me know if their team disagrees, which is something I appreciate and value

5.0
 5/5

Business Value

500,000 app members as of January 2023

$ 759.1K of attracted investments during the Pre-Seed round

Dozens of attracted affiliate partners – banks and investment companies

Expansion to Sweden and Finland as separate web applications 

M&A with AXO Group – one of the top European digital brokers for personal lending
